    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, this character gains a +1 bonus on <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Reflex\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reflex</a>&nbsp;saves made to avoid traps and a +1&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#dodge_bonus\" rel=\"nofollow\">dodge bonus</a>&nbsp;to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Armor-Class\" rel=\"nofollow\">armor class</a> against attacks made by traps. These bonuses increase by +1 every three levels thereafter (6th, 9th, 12th, 15th, and 18th level). Trap sense bonuses gained from multiple classes stack.</p>",
